1
00:00:17,839 --> 00:00:19,120
If you are not here

2
00:00:19,359 --> 00:00:20,640
when we come here so early,

3
00:00:20,640 --> 00:00:21,519
what should we do?

4
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:22,359
It's okay.

5
00:00:22,559 --> 00:00:23,320
We'll wait.

6
00:00:23,879 --> 00:00:24,719
Madam Yin.

7
00:00:25,920 --> 00:00:26,719
Madam Yin.

8
00:00:28,839 --> 00:00:30,239
She's coming out.

9
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:32,079
Great.

10
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:38,719
Madam Yin,

11
00:00:39,719 --> 00:00:40,840
the epidemic is now under control.

12
00:00:41,039 --> 00:00:43,200
We all appreciate your hard work.

13
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:45,600
Thank you for saving our lives.

14
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:47,640
Please accept

15
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:48,600
this small token of our gratitude.

16
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:50,520
I apologize to both of you.

17
00:00:51,119 --> 00:00:52,560
I was blinded by prejudice that day

18
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,520
and misunderstood your good intentions.

19
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,399
I almost lost my life

20
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:57,960
because of my bias.

21
00:00:58,799 --> 00:00:59,920
This is a small gift as a token of gratitude

22
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:00,799
and as an apology.

23
00:01:01,719 --> 00:01:02,520
Please accept it.

24
00:01:03,759 --> 00:01:04,599
As a healer,

25
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:07,359
it's my duty to treat

26
00:01:07,359 --> 00:01:08,560
and cure everyone.

27
00:01:09,159 --> 00:01:10,159
Seeing you all

28
00:01:10,159 --> 00:01:11,239
healthy and standing here,

29
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,519
I am very pleased.

30
00:01:13,799 --> 00:01:14,920
I accept your gratitude,

31
00:01:15,359 --> 00:01:16,200
but take the items back.

32
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,480
Please take it.

33
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,840
Go back.

34
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:21,239
You...

35
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:22,799
Thank you all for your kindness.

36
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,120
Please go back now.

37
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:24,959
Well,

38
00:01:25,799 --> 00:01:27,599
let's not force Madam Yin.

39
00:01:28,239 --> 00:01:29,239
Let's go back.

40
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:32,040
Thank you.

41
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,959
Healer Yin is truly a good person.

42
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,519
The Women's clinic is benevolent and helps the world.

43
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:48,599
What's wrong?

44
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:54,159
It's okay, don't cry.

45
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,680
It's okay, don't cry.

46
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,439
Don't cry, don't cry.

47
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,319
I'm happy.

48
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,799
We're happy too.

49
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:07,760
By the way, Yan Ge,

50
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,560
I have a gift for you too.

51
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:10,960
For me?

52
00:02:11,759 --> 00:02:12,520
Open it up.

53
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,639
What is it?

54
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:24,639
A divorce paper?

55
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:26,159
A divorce paper?

56
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:29,719
It's...

57
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:30,840
It's a divorce paper.

58
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,879
Now you can...

59
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,759
You all know it.

60
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:46,960
Sister Su,

61
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,439
then you...

62
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:49,800
Actually,

63
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,919
when Shen Yuan was arrested,

64
00:02:52,599 --> 00:02:53,800
I went to see him.

65
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:55,879
He refused to divorce,

66
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:57,280
so I beat him up.

67
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:16,520
My Lady,

68
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,039
it's time to take the medicine.

69
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,599
I'll do it.

70
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,240
You still

71
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,840
refuse to call me mother?

72
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:43,319
It's your rule.

73
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,319
I'm just following orders.

74
00:03:57,599 --> 00:04:00,000
I'm no longer the lady of the Xiao Family.

75
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,080
Shi'an,

76
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,840
you can call me mother.

77
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:07,439
He still cares about you.

78
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,479
He's just stubborn

79
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,960
and not good with words.

80
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:13,919
When the officials handed you over,

81
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:14,919
he got injured

82
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,120
trying to save you.

83
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,759
Let me see your wound.

84
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:22,839
It's just a minor injury.

85
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:24,319
I'm a healer.

86
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,160
I can take care of myself.

87
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:28,519
Your injuries are not healed yet.

88
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,600
You should take good care of yourself.

89
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,279
Take your medicine and get some rest.

90
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,560
The night is cool.

91
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,480
Don't make your illness worse.

92
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,160
Over the years,

93
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,959
I have failed you.

94
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:47,040
I really wanted you to stand out.

95
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:49,600
I don't want you to follow in my and your father's footsteps.

96
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:51,639
You have talent,

97
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:55,040
and shouldn't be confined to that small clinic.

98
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:58,959
Madam, there's no need to say more.

99
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,120
The past is the past.

100
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:03,439
Now that you've come to this,

101
00:05:04,439 --> 00:05:05,639
please take care of yourself.

102
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:13,439
In a few days,

103
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:14,879
when your wounds have healed,

104
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,000
I'll find a way to send you south,

105
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,399
far from Chang'an.

106
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,040
There,

107
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,959
you can start a new life.

108
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,160
I can't let this go.

109
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:25,639
I can't leave.

110
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:28,879
No one can protect you now.

111
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,199
Leaving is your only way out.

112
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:33,800
Don't be stubborn.

113
00:05:38,959 --> 00:05:41,000
He's thinking about you.

114
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,879
After all these years of planning,

115
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:47,000
how can I just

116
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:50,560
disappear into the misty south?

117
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:52,800
He doesn't understand.

118
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,160
This game has come to a point

119
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:58,839
where it can't end well.

120
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,240
My lord,

121
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:07,160
have any caravans headed south departed recently?

122
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,600
Especially those going beyond the Lingnan region?

123
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:10,360
Well,

124
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,079
there is one

125
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,680
leaving in three days,

126
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,040
taking the ancient road.

127
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:17,439
But with the strict inspections,

128
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,920
to get through the customs.

129
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:25,240
My Lord,

130
00:06:25,759 --> 00:06:27,120
this is far from enough.

131
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,040
How about...

132
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:32,439
This won't do.

133
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:34,000
This is a relic left by my father.

134
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,040
I can't give it to you.

135
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,800
I'll find a way to get the money.

136
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,319
I'll make up the shortfall within three days.

137
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:41,720
My Lord,

138
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,680
the most precious thing in this world is not jade,

139
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:46,439
but the human heart.

140
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:49,879
Three days.

141
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,000
I'll make sure you see the full amount.

142
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,240
Farewell.

143
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,600
Greetings, Madam.

144
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:32,839
This jade cicada of yours

145
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,240
is quite unique.

146
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,480
My father left this to me.

147
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,399
I'm not sure how to wear it properly.

148
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,439
It keeps falling out of my sleeve.

149
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:48,920
You...

150
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,360
Father?

151
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:54,519
Yes.

152
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,879
He gave it to me before he left.

153
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:03,040
Such a valuable item

154
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,399
should be well kept.

155
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:06,519
This must be something

156
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,720
that only the wealthy families

157
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,639
in Chang'an would have had in the past.

158
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,639
It's said to be passed down from my ancestors.

159
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:15,040
I must keep it safe.

160
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:17,800
It seems that your ancestors

161
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:19,360
were also

162
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,920
from a

163
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,519
distinguished family.

164
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:34,960
Sir,

165
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,279
I have realized my mistake.

166
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,840
Please let me go.

167
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:40,159
Don't be nervous.

168
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,399
I just have

169
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,919
one question for you.

170
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:47,960
Do you have any children?

171
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,480
I have a son and a daughter.

172
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:50,519
The younger one is just three.

173
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:51,879
And the older one?

174
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:53,039
Seven years old.

175
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,639
He looks just like his mother.

176
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:01,000
Do you know

177
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,840
Si Xiangting?

178
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,279
What?

179
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:05,399
It's nothing.

180
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:05,879
You can go now.

181
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:18,159
Si Xiangting's study tour is a cover.

182
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:20,000
His father was also a healer,

183
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,519
but passed away long ago.

184
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:22,559
Before,

185
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,279
he lived in a courtyard outside the city,

186
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,720
which belonged to the Liu family.

187
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,200
His birthdate

188
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:30,080
coincides with the time when Lady Liu

189
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,200
was secluded, nursing an illness.

190
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,159
Lady Liu's

191
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,600
illegitimate child?

192
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,000
It seems

193
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:39,840
Lady Liu got pregnant before marriage.

194
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,080
She didn't like his humble background,

195
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,080
so she came to my father.

196
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:48,039
If he has a relationship with her,

197
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:51,120
why has he been helping me all the time?

198
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:51,759
Besides,

199
00:09:52,039 --> 00:09:53,480
he never did anything

200
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,879
harmful to the Women's clinic.

201
00:09:58,279 --> 00:09:58,960
Have you forgotten

202
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,519
the arsenic that almost killed you

203
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,360
in the Metropolitan Court?

204
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,279
I've arranged for a caravan

205
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,480
heading south.

206
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,559
Just hide in the cargo box,

207
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:20,759
wrap yourself in black cloth,

208
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:22,320
and stay quiet.

209
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,639
I've told you,

210
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:24,919
I'm not leaving.

211
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,399
If you stay in Chang'an,

212
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,200
with all your crimes,

213
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:31,039
hanging is inevitable.

214
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:33,120
I saved you that day

215
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,799
to see you back in prison.

216
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,799
I don't want to see you

217
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,559
die either.

218
00:10:40,759 --> 00:10:41,600
If I leave,

219
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:42,679
what will you do?

220
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,039
Will you come with me?

221
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,399
I have unfinished business.

222
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,600
Once I've taken care of it,

223
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,200
I'll come south to find you.

224
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,159
Shi'an,

225
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,559
Could you call me that once more?

226
00:10:59,639 --> 00:11:00,159
Mother.

227
00:11:10,279 --> 00:11:11,120
Wait for me in the south.

228
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,159
It seems you all know.

229
00:11:45,919 --> 00:11:46,960
Why did you come to the Women's Clinic?

230
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,360
What was your purpose?

231
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:51,240
At first, she just wanted to

232
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,279
shut down the clinic.

233
00:11:53,279 --> 00:11:54,720
Later, I saw she had murderous intent towards you.

234
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,559
As a healer,

235
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,039
I couldn't turn a blind eye.

236
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,759
Seeing you all day and night in the clinic,

237
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,000
personally preparing every bowl of medicine,

238
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,840
every bowl of porridge,

239
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,159
even cleaning the most disgusting pus wounds,

240
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:09,039
you all run around for those women day and night,

241
00:12:10,279 --> 00:12:11,279
like a ray of light,

242
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:13,639
shining into the darkness I've never dared to face.

243
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,240
I began to hate the lies I told.

244
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,399
Then why

245
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:21,879
put arsenic in the medicine cabinet

246
00:12:22,559 --> 00:12:23,559
to frame me?

247
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,519
Perhaps,

248
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,759
because I share her blood,

249
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,879
I inherited her cruel nature.

250
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,639
She repeatedly reminded me

251
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,759
to remember my true identity.

252
00:12:36,799 --> 00:12:38,080
I am her only son.

253
00:12:39,679 --> 00:12:40,960
I understand your struggle.

254
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,240
It takes a lot of wandering

255
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:46,120
to break free from the shackles of blood ties.

256
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,440
Thank you.

257
00:12:47,759 --> 00:12:48,440
Lady Yin,

258
00:12:49,639 --> 00:12:50,600
you haven't

259
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,919
reprimanded me once.

260
00:12:53,759 --> 00:12:55,039
What's done is done.

261
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,639
Reprimanding is useless.

262
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,000
Sijun,

263
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,840
you don't have to be her son.

264
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,919
Everything you've done proves

265
00:13:02,919 --> 00:13:04,039
you will choose

266
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:05,320
conscience and light.

267
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,639
I've often tossed and turned,

268
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,000
wondering

269
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,519
if I were born into a different family,

270
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,879
I could have walked into the Women's Clinic

271
00:13:17,919 --> 00:13:18,879
and called you

272
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:20,960
sister openly.

273
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,519
But I took the wrong path.

274
00:13:24,519 --> 00:13:25,679
I will leave the Women's Clinic

275
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,399
and use my medical skills

276
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:29,159
to atone for my past sins.

277
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,600
It's also

278
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:34,000
a way to find my own path back.

279
00:13:36,919 --> 00:13:37,720
What about Yan Ge?

280
00:13:39,519 --> 00:13:40,879
Have you decided how to tell her?

281
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,039
I haven't decided yet.

282
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:54,480
Tomorrow,

283
00:13:56,519 --> 00:13:57,840
I'll also give her a clear explanation.
